title: 09/14: Start or Sit (NFC); CIN-BAL Recap; Week 3 Lookahead (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Recapping the surprising shootout in CIN at the top of the show and discussing the longterm values of basically every relevant player in the game. Will Alex Collins get the workload we were hoping for? Is Andy Dalton poised for a big season? ... Why Heath has Kirk Cousins ranked outside his Top 15 (12:50), news and notes from around the NFL including important RB updates (15:00), Beat the Waiver Wire for Week 3 (18:15) ... CAR-ATL (22:22), MIN-GB (27:03), IND-WAS (34:10), CLE-NO (41:00), PHI-TB (49:50), ARI-LAR (54:08), DET-SF (57:42), NYG-DAL (1:03:15) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
